{
  "stem": "16887.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a little-- a little village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It looked like it used to be maybe a summer camp or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were just shacks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when we got there, there was a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we took up residence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In one of the shacks was 10 of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was just board-- one board from the other was about two inches apart.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was snowing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But it was better than staying outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then we found out that, once a day, a-- I can't remember who it was-- used to bring hot soup.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the later part of December, because we left around the middle of December.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't even remember what the place was called like.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's-- that night, I remember all the men went to the village, to the farmers, to steal straw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They stole some straw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they brought it, and they put it up by the wall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And whoever went to sleep first-- we never undressed-- one next to the other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's how we lived there, maybe for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe more, I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then somebody came and said that we could register to go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That they have-- that they're going to have a transport, and they'll take us through Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We registered, and they took us to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They brought us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I can't remember how long we were traveling in those cattle wagons, maybe a week, maybe less.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because it's been so long, I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, we were not treated at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were on our own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the train stopped on the station-- which stopped more than was going, because the German's aeroplanes were chasing the transits.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
